content.raw:
My interpretation is that this PR is specifically for changing a test sdf file to use the newly introduced parameter for DART, which is analogous to a parameter that is already being used by ODE. After this is merged, we will then need to merge pull request #2755 before the new parameter can actually be used.

If that interpretation is correct, then I approve this PR.
